[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "刚刚还如同活物般的藤蔓和花朵，此时零落了一地。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "庄园恢复了往日的景象。米拉身上的装甲也失去了生机，尽数脱落在地上。她本人则因为脱力而跪倒在地，只能怨恨地盯着我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我走上前，捡起一片装甲。装甲上还残存着一部分泰坦物质，看样子是某种结合了泰坦物质和植物的生化装甲。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "米拉女士，现在我们能好好谈了吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_mira_01",
        "zh_CN": "……海姆达尔的队员确实名不虚传。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_mira_02",
        "zh_CN": "你呢？playername？你还和以前一样吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……我就觉得我们以前见过。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如果是在去空间站之前的话……抱歉，有些事情我记不清了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_mira_03",
        "zh_CN": "在不懂得怜香惜玉这一点上，和以前没什么变化嘛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我们以前较量过？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_mira_04",
        "zh_CN": "当然。我那时候还小，在你身上吃了点儿教训。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_mira_05",
        "zh_CN": "怎么样，这么些年，有长进吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_mira_06",
        "zh_CN": "你也看到了，以我现在的实力，你恐怕打不赢我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……激将法没用。我没动手是因为有点欺负你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "算了，总得让你见识一下，不然你不会放心把克罗瑞娜交给我的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我走到她面前，握住她体表残留的装甲，像漩涡一样，把泰坦物质吸了个空。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "米拉也察觉到了这一点。她睁大眼睛，紧盯着我的手和她手腕上的装甲接触的地方。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_mira_07",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "对手是我的话，你精心设计的战斗装甲就只能亮个相。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "本来不想说破这一点的，你毕竟是克罗瑞娜的长辈。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但你好像对我的误解有点深……所以，得罪了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不知道这种巨大的落差给米拉带来了多少伤害。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "克罗瑞娜，把项链给我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "接过克罗瑞娜解下的项链。项链上的宝石内也能感受到泰坦物质的存在。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我把项链递给米拉。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "猜得没错的话，岛上的实验室是在研究泰坦技术吧？米拉教授？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我当然不会忘记——米拉的另一个身份是卫城学院泰坦科技研究院的教授。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "自带电子攻击功能的植物，利用泰坦物质传递信息的机关——所以搜救队才能那么快到达荒岛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "自始至终，我都没有见过那个实验室。项目，技术，对我来说不重要了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "克罗瑞娜的项链就先由你保管，也希望你能相信我，把克罗瑞娜交给我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "米拉怔怔地看着项链。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "克罗瑞娜从我身后走了过来，在米拉的面前蹲下，抱住了自己的小姨。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "克罗瑞娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_girl022_01",
        "zh_CN": "对不起，小姨。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "克罗瑞娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_girl022_02",
        "zh_CN": "这里永远是我的家，你也永远是我的亲人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "克罗瑞娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_girl022_03",
        "zh_CN": "我只是想出去看看。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "克罗瑞娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_girl022_04",
        "zh_CN": "别伤心，好吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "米拉还是没有说话。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她低下头，攥紧了手里的项链。然后轻轻推开克罗瑞娜，转过身，步履蹒跚地往回走去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一周后。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "米拉回到家，习惯性地看了一眼楼梯。克罗瑞娜以前总是站在那个地方等她回家。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "即使过了一周了，她还是没能改掉这个习惯。每次望了个空，她都默默叹一口气。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她去了一趟荒岛上的实验室，重要的东西果然还在那里。于是她心里更难受了，只觉得抬不起头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "平时教导克罗瑞娜的时间空了下来，她感到无所事事。坐在沙发上，一时有些心酸。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "桌子上放着几封信，是这几天克罗瑞娜寄来的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "犹豫再三，她拆开了信封。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一张照片滑了出来——夹着滑蛋和牛肉的面包，旁边放着两杯加了冰块的牛奶。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "照片的背后写着几行小字：",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_girl022_05",
        "zh_CN": "小姨，这是我和playername的早餐。我亲手做的哦！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_girl022_06",
        "zh_CN": "做饭是一件令人开心的事。食材的搭配，烹饪的火候，调味的复合程度……都是要考虑的东西。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_girl022_07",
        "zh_CN": "为了让品尝者快乐而进行烹饪，所以每个步骤都灌注了心意。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_girl022_08",
        "zh_CN": "您曾经说过，做不擅长的事是在浪费时间……我觉得不对。playername吃得很开心，那一刻我很满足。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_girl022_09",
        "zh_CN": "等我回家的时候，也想做给您尝尝！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "米拉面无表情地看着这几行字，又把照片反转过来，仔细看照片里的食物。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "过了一会儿，她把照片放下，拆开了下一封信。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "依旧是一张照片。照片里是十指相扣的手——似乎是坐在副驾的playername拍的。路前方是夕阳，路和两侧的风景都披着金色的光影。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_girl022_10",
        "zh_CN": "小姨，忘了告诉您，playername送了我一辆房车。我们正开着它去霍尔姆。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_girl022_11",
        "zh_CN": "我喜欢开车——我总觉得踩下动力踏板时的推背感具现了整个时代的科技。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_girl022_12",
        "zh_CN": "风景真好。看一千遍视频也比不上亲眼看一次。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_girl022_13",
        "zh_CN": "太阳升起的时候，整条路上只有我们。我表达不出那种感觉。如果有机会，我也想带您看看。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_mira_08",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米拉",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_mira_09",
        "zh_CN": "开车也不专心。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "米拉喃喃自语着，又拆开了下一封信。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这次的信里除了照片还有一枚银币。照片是playername和克罗瑞娜的合影。两个人站在一座山城的主道上，对着镜头微笑。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_girl022_14",
        "zh_CN": "小姨，我收到了一枚银币，想把它送给你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_girl022_15",
        "zh_CN": "路过这座城市的时候，有人请我帮忙拍个照。她很欣赏我的拍照技术，执意要给我钱。我没有收，她就送了我这个。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_girl022_16",
        "zh_CN": "我也许可以做一个厨子，一个摄影师，或者一个司机。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_girl022_17",
        "zh_CN": "playername说，海姆达尔队员的待遇很丰厚。我不知道丰厚是指多少，总之，我大概是饿不死的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc31ep9_girl022_18",
        "zh_CN": "我也不知道我想说什么。想到哪就写到哪了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
